data.description: SERENITY, SECURITY, SPENDOR all that and more in this log home ON 5 ACRES.   You can be in by Christmas and enjoy a cracklin fire in the fireplace in the soaring ceilings while the children look down from the loft above.  Master suite on the main level everyone will love this home.  Bring all your big boy toys to the over 1300sq ft garage. Hurry and move in tomorrow.
data.whatILove: Peaceful setting with beautiful views from every angle of this home.  The over 1300 sq ft detached garage with workshop area is just a dream for the woodworker, mechanic, or craftsman.  There is so much to love with the stamped concrete patios leading out to the screen house complete with ceiling fan for entertaining or just relaxing.  This home is one you will never want to leave. The neighborhood offers a lake for fishing.
